{"tid":1942474,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡卓妍鍾欣潼Full Gear 保護衣（戲服）返港","createTime":"2020-03-25T05:44:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T05:58:00.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"07e86c63d14a061393b459f5586397f8e422bc32","tid":1942474,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T05:44:38.000Z","msg":"蔡卓妍（阿Sa）、鍾欣潼（阿嬌）、關智斌（Kenny）、陳家樂、何珮瑜（Jeana）及黃德斌於馬來西亞趕拍網劇《女法醫JD》，因全球新冠肺炎疫情爆發，原定4月中才拍畢，但當地都需要停工避炎，所以一眾演員決定先行「撤離」回港，眾人將面對14日家居隔離。阿Sa、阿嬌、Kenny、家樂、Jeana等晚上抵港，更穿上全副防疫裝備，包括白色保護衣、口罩及保護面罩，各人手上亦已戴上電子手帶。<br />\n<br />\n講到回港心情，阿Sa表示：「由於馬來西亞嗰邊好多嘢唔開，所以我哋就要暫時停工，公司就叫我哋返嚟先。」Kenny說：「返咗嚟先，費事無了期，唔知等到幾時。」提到返港後要強制隔離14天，陳家樂說：「都冇乜分別，因為我哋喺嗰邊都係隔離，喺屋企隔離會開心啲。馬來西亞疫情開始嚴重，所以冇乜落街。」阿嬌說：「冇落過街。」阿Sa亦謂：「我哋住嗰個區好啲，少啲人，之前喺吉隆坡會多人啲。」問到隔離的日子會做甚麼？阿Sa和Kenny表示買了跑步機，準備在家中做運動！<br />\n<br />\n問到在飛機上可有擔心？阿Sa說：「好彩套劇我係演法醫，做鑑證工作。（戲服嚟？）係戲服，同佢哋（指劇組）借住先，如果唔係邊買得到，好彩咋！」眾人表示在機上4小時，全程沒有去廁所、進食及飲水。<br />\n據知，英皇特別買了新冠肺炎快速測試產品，供阿Sa、阿嬌等眾星使用，以確保他們的健康及安全，因為保護自己之餘，都要保護身邊其他人！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200324/photo/bkn-20200324233115019-0324_00862_001_01p.jpg?20200325002437\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200324%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200324233115019-0324_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20200325002437&h=8058fa6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200324/photo/bkn-20200324233115019-0324_00862_001_04p.jpg?20200325002437\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200324%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200324233115019-0324_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20200325002437&h=687b0115&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200324/photo/bkn-20200324233115019-0324_00862_001_03p.jpg?20200325002437\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200324%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200324233115019-0324_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20200325002437&h=59633662&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"976bcb2d982802818d3191a993c663bb6d0b5cec","tid":1942474,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T05:53:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48befb57e0f44245cce50319136c076d6aa7eb3","tid":1942474,"uid":153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T05:54:55.000Z","msg":"個肺都黑色 驚咩肺炎"},{"pid":"fdaf2a89a22a38a809fae7d106b8e3df2a595a43","tid":1942474,"uid":214502,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T05:55:05.000Z","msg":"個牛肺咁黑 中肺炎變番白佢"},{"pid":"11e5e119fc588d125069c82c100e8c52e3990dfb","tid":1942474,"uid":57674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f48befb57e0f44245cce50319136c076d6aa7eb3","tid":1942474,"uid":153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T05:54:55.000Z","msg":"個肺都黑色 驚咩肺炎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T05:56:56.000Z","msg":"驚變返白"},{"pid":"ef243c489e773024c1301869e14272d15ba22f71","tid":1942474,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T05:57:19.000Z","msg":"點解唔係落機即刻除左dum左件衫<br />\n如果有菌咪痴晒返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d5caa24f4c07ffcaf7eca2d4eb3c598a5764860","tid":1942474,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef243c489e773024c1301869e14272d15ba22f71","tid":1942474,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T05:57:19.000Z","msg":"點解唔係落機即刻除左dum左件衫<br />\n如果有菌咪痴晒返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T05:58:00.000Z","msg":"冇所謂啦 唔係害到人就得"}]}